<p>Import results :</p>
<ul>
	<li><!-- TMPL_VAR name="imported" --> imported records</li>
	<li><!-- TMPL_VAR name="alreadyindb" --> not imported because already in catalog</li>
	<li><!-- TMPL_VAR name="alreadyinfarm" --> not imported because already in the reservoir</li>
